X200机器上的MySqlServer root P X200sql2017
$mysql -u root -p X200sql2017
1 CREATE DATABASE nltkdb;
2 CREATE USER 'nluser'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'nltkDB2017!';
3 GRANT ALL ON nltkdb.* TO 'nluser'@'localhost';
4 FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
创建数据库nltkdb，并赋权给nluser，pass：nltkDB2017!
mysql> show databases;
mysql> use nltkdb; 
mysql> show tables;

$sudo apt install mysql-workbench

$mysql-workbench 启动图形界面的mysql-workbench：



